---
title: Makrut Lime Coconut Fish with Garlic Rice & Zesty Coconut
description: We’re going nuts for this aromatic coconut sauce infused with the citrus of makrut lime leaves. Top golden white fish and steamed veggies with this saucy delight and let the garlic rice soak up the rest for a spectacular finish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/makrut-lime-coconut-fish-dbae8693.jpg
